## 📈 What to watch for

| Signal | Target | What it tells you |
|---|---|---|
| Profile completion rate | 70%+ of trial signups complete "Your Voice" | New framing is landing |
| First-session plan generation rate | 60%+ of profile-completers generate a plan | Onboarding is converting |
| Customer support emails mentioning "strategist" or "thinking" | Increasing over time | In-app positioning reinforcing marketing positioning |
| Re-generation frequency | Decreasing over time | Voice matching is improving + onboarding is working |
| Time spent in "Your Voice" profile | 2-4 minutes average | Users taking voice training seriously |

If profile completion drops below 50%, the new "Your Voice" framing may be too long. Consider compressing.

If re-generation rates stay high, voice matching isn't working — which is a product issue, not a copy issue.

